<div type="translation"><ab>
			<lb n="1"/>
		Au nom de Dieu, clément [et miséricordieux !]
		In the name of God, the Compassionate, [the Merciful].
			<lb n="2"/>
		De la part de ʿAbd al-Malik b. Ya[zīd. Au maître  de poste d&#039;Ašmūn].
		From ʿAbd al-Malik bn Mar[wān to the postmaster of Ashmūn].
			<lb n="3"/>
		Donne à ʿAbd al-Ḥamīd [le messager de ... b. ...]
		Give ʿAbd al-Ḥamīd, [my messenger, … who is]
			<lb n="4"/>
		a fair, handsome youth, t[wo post mounts],
		jeune homme, petit et b[lan]c, deux montures de la poste],
			<lb n="5"/>
		dont l&#039;une est celle [du courrier. ... a écrit en]
		one of them the [post guide’s] mount. [Written by … in the month]
			<lb n="6"/>
		of Shawwāl, in the year [one hundred and thirty-]one.
		šawwāl l&#039;année [cent quarante-et]-un.
			<lb n="8"/>
		[De la part de ʿAbd al-Malik b. Yazīd. Au]     maître de poste d&#039;Ašmūn.
		[From ʿAbd al-Malik bn Marwān to] the post master of Ashmūn.
</ab></div>
